<p>老师们现场答疑~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/23bb1f33b07244d4a4b1fe174303c33c.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>同学们超级认真的哦~</p>
<p><strong>回顾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本次讲座分为四部分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Donna学姐为大家展示博士生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Rachel学姐给大家分享她申博的经验</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Lan老师带大家了解申博的各个环节和时间点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后还有自由答疑环节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/4cc8262cfa0046b391b68f0d3ebba2bd.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/e54da4301a554f83810fdc2884fc5570.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>博士生活大揭秘</strong></p>
<p>Donna学姐不仅分享了博士四年的日常，还对之后的就业问题阐述了自己的想法。对于那些不清楚读博生活的同学们，Donna的讲解是不是让你们明朗很多呢？读博能得到什么？读博需要具备什么能力？都是需要好好思考，好好下决心的！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/98c8a12795f84b3980f66626bf90c2ef.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>Start: become a Ph.D Student</strong></p>
<p><strong>第一年：Confirmation Review（9-18个月）</strong></p>
<p>Literature Review</p>
<p>一些必修和选修课：</p>
<p>DDP (Doctoral Training Plan)</p>
<p>完成开题报告</p>
<p>参加开题报告答辩</p>
<p>TNA (Training Analysis)</p>
<p><strong>第二年：Data collection</strong></p>
<p>确定研究方法</p>
<p>Fieldwork/Experiments</p>
<p>数据分析</p>
<p><strong>第三年：Writing-up</strong></p>
<p><strong>第四年：Viva</strong></p>
<p>Viva的形式（Q&amp;A with internal examiner and external examiner)</p>
<p>Viva的时长（3个小时-the whole day)</p>
<p>Viva的结果（no correction, minor correction, major correction, fail) 3-12个月修改时间，resubmit</p>
<p>博士申请流程及注意事项</p>
<p>Rachel学姐根据自己，还有帮助曼汉教育的学生申请的经验，给大家做了精彩的分享~ 干货满满哟！特别是面试和与老师的沟通方面，Rachel都有很独到的见解呢~Rachel学姐作为曼汉教育的优秀博士Tutor，她的很多学生已经拿到明年的准offer了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/2635bd4adaa24139b4cf1e06cfeec574.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/cd7d19c19fa6490f87511a9d84e6cabc.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/f74ef9860e3042e3bf4957ed0761ea4f.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>海外博士申请过程及时间规划</p>
<p>Lan老师根据她丰富的申博经验，给大家全方位展示了申博的重点：申请过程、时间规划、读博费用、奖学金渠道。另外还有海外各国的不同情况，Lan老师有问必答哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/994e64edfc334a7ca2031866f8d7082d.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/798712022972445196ca06e68b139ece.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/a90d51160f734bb18778a780b3280fa1.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/96349a76241b4640a92a8ac57b10c58a.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>答疑环节</strong></p>
<p>还有现场答疑，场面火爆哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191020/e3a493bb8cd94014a556f3d5dd9d4400.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
